 word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n vs Thanh H\u00f3a: 3-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111ang th\u0103ng hoa v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 5 tr\u1eadn b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Nh\u1edd phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f3 m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 tr\u00ean BXH v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng, Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a c\u00f3 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ngo\u1ea1i binh Faye v\u00e0 Ofere \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng khi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p t\u1edbi 13 trong s\u1ed1 25 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, \u1edf chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 12 tr\u00ean BXH v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 (TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh) \u0111\u00fang 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, CLB c\u1ee7a HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, c\u1ea3 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0111\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Trong 7 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 13 trong s\u1ed1 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y, s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f2n s\u1edf h\u1eefu ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ngo\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m l\u00e0 Da Sylva. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mauritania \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 16 tr\u1eadn, x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 trong danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 sau Oseni c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 28 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p h\u01a1n 1/3 s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i V-League, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, 2 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t, Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\n+ S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: V\u0103n Phong (GK), Ng\u1ecdc H\u00e0o, V\u0103n Ng\u1ecd, \u0110\u1ee9c L\u1ee3i, Ng\u1ecdc Duy, Ho\u00e0ng Thi\u00ean, Xu\u00e2n D\u01b0\u01a1ng, V\u0103n Tri\u1ec1n, Anh V\u0169, V\u0169 T\u00edn, Da Sylva.<br>\r\n+ Thanh H\u00f3a: Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (GK), \u0110\u00ecnh \u0110\u1ed3ng, V\u0103n Nam, Minh T\u00f9ng, Xu\u00e2n H\u01b0ng, Tr\u1ecdng Ho\u00e0ng, Ho\u00e0ng Th\u1ecbnh, Minh Tu\u1ea5n, H\u1eefu D\u0169ng, Faye, \u0110\u00ecnh T\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"990","checkdouble":"190581"},{"date":"09:40 07/07","title":"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Uruguay b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau sai l\u1ea7m t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/thu-mon-uruguay-bi-chi-trich-sau-sai-lam-te-hai-truoc-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Gary Neville \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Fernando Muslera sau sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u00e1ch \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.</h2><h2>Muslera m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Muslera m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Gary Neville h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Muslera m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m, nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 t\u1eeb Gary Neville h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/thu-mon-uruguay-bi-chi-trich-sau-sai-lam-te-hai-truoc-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Muslera m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi\u1ebfn Uruguay thua Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raphael Varane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t. V\u00e0 \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Didier Deschamps \u0111\u00e3 nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00f4i c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t \u1edf ph\u00fat 61 khi Muslera kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00fa s\u00fat t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i hi\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Griezmann.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Atletico Madrid \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eb3ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Muslera. Thay v\u00ec b\u1eaft g\u1ecdn, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Uruguay l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng ra ngo\u00e0i. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng b\u1eadt l\u00ean tr\u1eddi r\u1ed3i \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Muslera</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-uruguay-vs-phap-461-190537.html\" target=\"_blank\">Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p</span>, Neville \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u00e1ch m\u00f3c th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Uruguay. B\u1edfi n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u0129 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u1eadu ta \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch ngu ng\u1ed1c. \u0110\u00e1ng l\u1ebd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9. N\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 bom.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i c\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ed3i. Th\u1eadt ra t\u00f4i c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. B\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i c\u1ee7a c\u00fa s\u00fat kh\u00f4ng tr\u00f9ng v\u1edbi h\u01b0\u1edbng nh\u00ecn c\u1ee7a Muslera. L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p \u0111\u1ec3 tay l\u1ecdt ra kh\u1ecfi t\u1ea7m m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMuslera \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 sai t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh. \u1ede tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi 100 c\u00fa s\u00fat nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u1ea3 100 qu\u1ea3. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1eb7t tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u1ef1c v\u00e0 b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec c\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cGriezmann \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0103n m\u1eebng pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u01a1i x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-diem-nhan-sau-chien-thang-20-cua-phap-truoc-uruguay-421-190559.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-uruguay-vs-phap-461-190537.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Uruguay 0-2 Ph\u00e1p (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"989","checkdouble":"190582"},{"date":"09:22 07/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 8/7): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/nhan-dinh-nga-vs-croatia-1h00-ngay-87-co-hoi-nao-cho-chu-nha.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u0169ng g\u1ee3i nh\u1eafc v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi ho\u00e0ng kim c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c2u.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi anh em<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 tan r\u00e3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ed1i x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 ngh\u0129a \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c2u v\u00e0o th\u1eadp ni\u00ean 90 c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u00e9o theo m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 trong khu v\u1ef1c, m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00e1ch ra t\u1eeb sau s\u1ef1 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u loay hoay t\u00ecm ra l\u1ed1i \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh huy ho\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 87) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 87) C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Nga-vs-Croatia.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia: Li\u1ec7u c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd?</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia n\u00e0y, Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t. T\u00e1ch ra t\u1eeb Nam T\u01b0 c\u0169, Croatia \u0111i t\u1edbi t\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 1998, k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean &quot;Vatreni&quot; tham d\u1ef1 v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u1ed9c l\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c2u l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau khi kh\u1ed1i XHCN t\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng World Cup 2018 l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0110\u00f4ng \u00c2u l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u1ebd trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Vi\u1ec7c Nga vs Croatia ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nhau \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u00fap m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. V\u1edbi Croatia, th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 Luka Modric c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 Davor Suker t\u1eebng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f2n 20 n\u0103m v\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966, khi h\u1ecd v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a Li\u00ean X\u00f4.</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng Nga r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng y\u1ebfu th\u1ebf h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao nh\u1edd l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Modric v\u00e0 Rakitic - nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u hi\u1ec7n nay.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nga va Croatia deu so huu nhung trung phong co the hinh an tuong la Dzyuba va Mandzukic.\" title=\"Nga v\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng trung phong c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 Dzyuba v\u00e0 Mandzukic.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/dyuba-vs-mandzukic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Nga v\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng trung phong c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 Dzyuba v\u00e0 Mandzukic.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n gi\u1ed1ng nhau khi \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng nhi\u1ec1u sang bi\u00ean, sau \u0111\u00f3 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb bi\u00ean v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 uy hi\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng trung phong c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng, ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian cho \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 Atem Dzyuba (Nga) v\u00e0 Mario Mandzukic (Croatia).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, Croatia c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y b\u00f3ng cho tuy\u1ebfn hai d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. T\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, 4 trong s\u1ed1 8 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i to\u00e1n c\u1ea7n HLV Cherchesov gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed9c h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Fisht Olympic.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Nga v\u00e0 Croatia t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p nhau 3 l\u1ea7n. Hai trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Euro 2008 v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng bnf th\u1eafng. Tr\u1eadn c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 cho Croatia \u1edf giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11/2015.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* S\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng Croatia ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y (8) ngang v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2006 v\u00e0 2014 c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Nga c\u00f3 10 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng trong hai tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, 1 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n (Dzyuba vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* 10 trong 12 b\u00e0n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup \u0111\u1ebfn trong hi\u1ec7p hai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">* Mario Mandzukic \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup cho \u0110T Croatia, ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m Davor Suker (6).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng:</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nga:</strong> Alan Dzagoev, Yuri Zhirkov ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Croatia:</strong> Ivan Strinic ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc ra s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nga vs Croatia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 8/7):</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nga (4-2-3-1): </strong>1.Akinfeev - 2.Fernandes, 3.Kutepov, 4.Ignashevich, 13.Kudryashov - 8.Gazinskiy, 11.Zobnin - 19.Samedov, 17.Golovin, 6.Cheryshev - 22.Dzyuba</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Croatia (4-5-1): </strong>23.Subasic - 2.Vrsaljko, 21.Vida, 6.Lovren, 3.Strinic - 18.Rebic, 10.Modric, 11.Brozovic, 7.Rakitic, 4.Perisic - 17.Mandzukic</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1:</strong> Nga 1-1 Croatia (Nga th\u1eafng tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Nga vs Croatia\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nga vs Croatia\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/073513-Nga-vs-Croatia-(4-2-3-1-vs-4-5-1).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Nga vs Croatia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Nga v\u00e0 Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-3-cau-thu-gay-that-vong-nhat-cua-dt-tay-ban-nha-466-190435.html\">World Cup 2018: 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-chiec-giay-vang-goi-ten-ai-421-190348.html\">C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng g\u1ecdi t\u00ean ai?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hang-hot-tuyen-nga-tiep-tuc-ban-tin-hieu-cho-chelsea-421-190313.html\">H\u00e0ng hot tuy\u1ec3n Nga ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1eafn t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u cho Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/luka-modric-ngon-co-dau-cua-nguoi-croatia-389-190104.html\">Luka Modric: Ng\u1ecdn c\u1edd \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/khong-phai-modric-hay-rakitic-linh-hon-cua-croatia-la-ai-421-189917.html\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i Modric hay Rakitic, linh h\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Croatia l\u00e0 ai?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-croatia-vs-dan-mach-463-190116.html\">Croatia 1-1 (pen 3-2) \u0110an M\u1ea1ch (KT): L\u00ednh ch\u00ec b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i d\u00f9 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"988","checkdouble":"190583"},{"date":"10:21 07/07","title":"5 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/5-ly-do-giup-bi-vuot-qua-brazil-de-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u201cQu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf\u201d chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb Nam M\u0129.</h2><h2>Martinez t\u00ecm ra h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV&nbsp;Roberto Martinez t\u00ecm ra h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>, B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 5 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Brazil, HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt 4-3-3. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i v\u1edbi s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ebft c\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 3 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Brazil. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Fellaini v\u00e0 Witsel, B\u1ec9 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi &ldquo;c\u00e2y \u0111inh ba&rdquo; b\u00ean ph\u00eda Selecao b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n khu trung tuy\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, De Bruyne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao h\u01a1n. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i d\u00e2ng l\u00ean ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng Lukaku v\u00e0 Hazard. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a De Bruyne c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 v\u00e0 gi\u00fap c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng linh ho\u1ea1t, B\u1ec9 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Ph\u00e1p ph\u1ea3i \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n v\u00e0o tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Brazil nh\u1edb Casemiro\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"casemiro tha vang truoc Brazil\" title=\"casemiro tha vang truoc Brazil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Willian-phat-bieu-ve-Brazil-sau-chien-thang-truoc-Mexico-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Casemiro v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00ec \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Casemiro kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Brazil. Fernandinho l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thay th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Anh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn Selecao th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n thua th\u1ee9 hai, Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Brazil kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o cho De Bruyne l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. Fernandinho \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t t\u00edch ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u1edf pha b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00f3. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Casemiro c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Lukaku nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ch\u1eb7n \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi k\u1ecbp l\u00e0m n\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n.</div>\r\n<h2>De Bruyne v\u00e0 Hazard ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne Hazard\" title=\"De Bruyne Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/101748-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>De Bruyne v\u00e0 Hazard \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7y c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t ch\u00fang nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhau. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Martinez, h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm cho t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil. Nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh, B\u1ec9 v\u1eabn ch\u01a1i v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1eabn d\u1eaft b\u1edfi hai ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi l\u00e0 Hazard v\u00e0 De Bruyne.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Bruyne l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i ch\u00f3i s\u00e1ng trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c x\u00e9 n\u00e1t h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Brazil. Ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i l\u00f9i s\u00e2u theo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Roberto Martinez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Hazard c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i khi De Bruyne ch\u01a1i d\u00e2ng cao. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i cho Fagner trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00e0 \u1edf 20 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 B\u1ec9 tr\u1edf n\u00ean r\u1ec7u r\u00e3 m\u1ecfi m\u1ec7t, Hazard ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. Anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng d\u1ed3n d\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Brazil.</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois th\u0103ng hoa\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois\" title=\"Courtois\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/5.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Courtois d\u01b0\u1edbn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ebft c\u1ee1 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Neymar</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Courtois \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 ai nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Courtois, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i suy ngh\u0129 sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a anh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil \u0111\u00eam qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCourtois ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, Brazil c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 27 c\u00fa s\u00fat \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Courtois c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCourtois ng\u0103n Coutinho ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t pha c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Neymar c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00f3 tay khi c\u00fa s\u00fat v\u00e0o g\u00f3c ch\u1ebft c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn b\u1ecb th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd pha bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Courtois \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 pha c\u1ee9u thua hay nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup 2018 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<h2>Neymar ch\u1ec9 gi\u1ecfi \u0103n v\u1ea1\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Neymar\" title=\"Neymar\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Neymar ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Neymar d\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong b\u1ed9 ba MSN b\u00e1 ch\u1ee7 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u1ee7a Barcelona. V\u00e0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Neymar c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do PSG b\u1ecf ra t\u1edbi g\u1ea7n 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn Neymar v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha \u0103n v\u1ea1 th\u00f4 thi\u1ec3n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 14 ph\u00fat n\u1eb1m l\u0103n ra s\u00e2n trong 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u. Anh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 2 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ng\u00e3 v\u1edd l\u1ed9 li\u1ec5u trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi B\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec9nh cao nh\u1ea5t. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Neymar v\u1eabn c\u00f2n bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng th\u00ec Neymar c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec c\u00f2n Brazil ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brazil-12-bi-421-190565.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"987","checkdouble":"190585"},{"date":"11:06 07/07","title":"Paulinho: \"Thua B\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn thua \u0110\u1ee9c 1-7\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/paulinho-thua-bi-con-dau-don-hon-tran-thua-duc-17.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Paulinho cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn thua \u0110\u1ee9c 1-7 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m.</h2><h2>Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Tite b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span>. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, Selecao \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0110\u1ee9c h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1-7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 Paulinho, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn thua l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Brazil t\u1ea1i Belo Horizonte cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 v\u1eeba qua c\u00f2n kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paulinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u Thua B\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn thua \u0110\u1ee9c 1-7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paulinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u Thua B\u1ec9 c\u00f2n \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn thua \u0110\u1ee9c 1-7 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/paulinho-thua-bi-con-dau-don-hon-tran-thua-duc-17.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Paulinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi Brazil b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cV\u1edbi t\u00f4i, c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 h\u00f4m nay th\u00ec mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u00e1ch m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean ch\u00e2n h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Jesus c\u0169ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Jesus c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Brazil. Anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Nga l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1ecb b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t trong c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Brazil nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed1t tr\u1ea7m \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi Jesus th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i Man City m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi 13 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eadn l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i hy sinh nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 World Cup. Ai c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1. Nh\u01b0ng sau m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft, n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 \u0110T\u00a0Brazil:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/5-ly-do-giup-bi-vuot-qua-brazil-de-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-466-190585.html\">5 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"986","checkdouble":"190586"},{"date":"11:17 07/07","title":"Meunier khi\u00eau kh\u00edch: \"T\u00f4i t\u01b0\u1edfng Neymar \u0111\u00e1 hay l\u1eafm\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/meunier-khieu-khich-toi-tuong-neymar-da-hay-lam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thomas Meunier kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Neymar t\u1ea1i Kazan Arena.</h2><h2>Neymar im ti\u1ebfng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Fernandinho c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u0103ng nh\u01b0 k\u1ebb ch\u1ec9 c\u1ee7a De Bruyne \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1 t\u1ea1i Kazan. Tuy c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a Renato Augusto trong hi\u1ec7p hai nh\u01b0ng Selecao kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Courtois m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t pha c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0o g\u00f3c ch\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y th\u0103ng hoa, Courtois \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u01b0\u1edbn ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Meunier n\u1ed5 to\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Meunier d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u Neymar sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Meunier d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u Neymar sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Brazil h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/meunier-khieu-khich-toi-tuong-neymar-da-hay-lam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Meunier d\u00e8 b\u1ec9u Neymar sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\" target=\"_blank\">Brazil vs B\u1ec9</span> \u0111\u00eam qua, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Meunier \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao Neymar. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi Neymar kh\u00f4ng \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho anh nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat to\u00e1t m\u1ed3 h\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn chung, h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1eafn k\u1ebft v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi nhau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i lu\u00f4n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap t\u1eeb Marouane Fellaini c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Toby Alderweireld. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c khi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n Neymar, Coutinho hay Marcelo. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng nhau v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 hay tr\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i hy sinh kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng vui m\u1eebng v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 hy sinh \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/5-ly-do-giup-bi-vuot-qua-brazil-de-vao-ban-ket-world-cup-2018-466-190585.html\">5 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"985","checkdouble":"190587"},{"date":"07:06 07/07","title":"\"Fellaini l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 h\u1ea1 Brazil\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/fellaini-la-nguyen-nhan-giup-bi-ha-brazil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Marouane Fellaini, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Selecao \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rio Ferdinand \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Marouane Fellaini</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Brazil 2-1, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00f2ng ph\u1eb3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-brazil-vs-bi-421-190550.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Brazil vs B\u1ec9 </span>gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Roberto Martinez l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p. C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Marouane Fellaini h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Marouane Fellaini h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/fellaini-la-nguyen-nhan-giup-bi-ha-brazil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Marouane Fellaini</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRio Ferdinand ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Marouane Fellaini, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n gi\u00fap B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Selecao \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cFellaini l\u00e0 con qu\u00e1i v\u1eadt n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Fernandinho b\u00ean ph\u00eda Brazil. Khi c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brazil c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng Fellaini theo s\u00e1t m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3, n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u00f9ng th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong tranh ch\u1ea5p\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNeymar \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Fellaini, th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh to l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Fellaini khi\u1ebfn s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a Brazil g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Neymar, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n phong t\u1ecfa r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Brazil. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Fellaini l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng\u201d</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Jurgen Klinsmann c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chung quan \u0111i\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ef1u HLV \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c Jurgen Klinsmann c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a Fellaini trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a B\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fellaini\" title=\"Fellaini\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/5/roberto-martinez-moi-hlv-deu-muon-co-mot-cau-thu-nhu-fellaini.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fellaini \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cBrazil \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng theo \u0111\u00fang \u00fd c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n l\u00e0 b\u1edfi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 to cao v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t. Neymar, Coutinho hay Jesus kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t, h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf so v\u1edbi B\u1ec9 trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111eo b\u00e1m r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brazil. Fellaini \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong hi\u1ec7p 1, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng gian c\u1ee7a Neymar v\u00e0 l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brazil. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"984","checkdouble":"190569"},{"date":"07:26 07/07","title":"Marcelo: \"T\u00f4i \u0111au c\u1ea3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c l\u1eabn t\u00e2m h\u1ed3n\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/marcelo-toi-dau-ca-the-xac-lan-tam-hon.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marcelo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9, ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i anh b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c l\u1eabn tinh th\u1ea7n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marcelo d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarcelo tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i do Marcelo \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m l\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a Brazil \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcelo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Marcelo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/marcelo-toi-dau-ca-the-xac-lan-tam-hon.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcelo b\u1ecb \u0111au trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00ednh v\u00ec vi\u1ec7c l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn Marcelo xu\u1ed1ng s\u1ee9c, c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 theo k\u1ecbp Eden Hazard trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i t\u0103ng t\u1ed1c.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng \u1ed1ng k\u00ednh m\u00e1y quay ghi l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Marcelo t\u1eadp t\u1ec5nh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n n\u1eefa nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thi \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarcelo ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9, ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t \u0111au \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i b\u1ecb t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Marcelo \u0111au c\u1ea3 t\u00e2m h\u1ed3n l\u1eabn th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-brazil-vs-bi-421-190550.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Brazil vs B\u1ec9</span> khi\u1ebfn Selecao nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Marcelo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eeba \u0111au v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u1ea1i v\u1eeba c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcelo that vong sau tran thua cua Brazil truoc Bi\" title=\"Marcelo th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/mace.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcelo th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Brazil tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong 15 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn di\u1ec5n ra c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng. Trong hi\u1ec7p 2, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00eam kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, h\u00f4m nay b\u1ea1n h\u01b0\u1edfng ni\u1ec1m vui, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u00e0y mai b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBrazil \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch. B\u1edfi v\u1eady vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"983","checkdouble":"190570"},{"date":"07:12 07/07","title":"H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Brazil, B\u1ec9 thi\u1ec7t qu\u00e2n nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/ha-guc-brazil-bi-thiet-quan-nghiem-trong-tai-vong-ban-ket.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi tr\u1ea3i qua chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Selecao, HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111ang m\u00e9o m\u1eb7t v\u00ec \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin bu\u1ed3n: h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thomas Meunier b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.\r\n</h2><h2>Meunier nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a FIFA, s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng t\u00edch l\u0169y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea9y tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp 1 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e3 s\u01b0u t\u1eadp 1 th\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft nh\u01b0 th\u01b0\u1eddng. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n c\u1ee7a Thomas Meunier trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Brazil.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi Neymar, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o PSG, Meunier \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec. Anh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi si\u00eau sao Brazil \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Meunier \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u, anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng 1 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thomas Meunier b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft\" title=\"Thomas Meunier b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/ha-guc-brazil-bi-thiet-quan-nghiem-trong-tai-vong-ban-ket.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thomas Meunier b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady, HLV Roberto Martinez s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, Meunier \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Ph\u00e1p l\u00e2u n\u0103m, ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn \u0110T B\u1ec9 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed wingback c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Yannick Carassco c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf b\u1edfi Nacer Chadli, B\u1ec9 l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e2n b\u00e0i \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Thomas Meunier. C\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng trong c\u00e1ch v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Ch\u1ec9 khi xoay sang 3-4-3 ho\u1eb7c m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 3-5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, \u0110T B\u1ec9 m\u1edbi ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Trong c\u1ea3 2 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0y, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Meunier trong vai tr\u00f2 wingback ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t quan tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Thomas Meunier b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2, HLV Martinez c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ra ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n kh\u00e1c, ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i xoay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin ch\u1eb1ng m\u1ea5y vui v\u1ebb tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Brazil 1-2 Bi\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Thong-so-Brazil.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi-421-190558.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-cau-dinh-cao-brazil-vs-bi-421-190558.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mong ch\u1edd nh\u1ea5t v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Brazil...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-brazil-vs-bi-461-190551.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Brazil 1-2 B\u1ec9 (T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nSau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Uruguay tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 Brazil c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 thua B\u1ec9 1-2. M\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Tite tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"982","checkdouble":"190571"},{"date":"07:06 07/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (7/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-772018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay 7/7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u00f4ng tin ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra h\u00f4m nay v\u00e0 \u0111\u00eam/r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y mai.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/3/Lich_thi_dau_World_Cup_2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vck-world-cup-2018/lich-thi-dau-41.html\"> L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK World Cup 2018 m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t</span><br>\r\nC\u1eadp nh\u1eadt nhanh ch\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u VCK World Cup 2018 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 14.6 \u0111\u1ebfn 15.7.2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/anh-vs-thuy.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"1\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: bold; background-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Ng\u00e0y gi\u1edd</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: bold; background-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u</td>\r\