div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup \u2013 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ecba t\u1ed1i cao \u0111\u00f3 su\u1ed1t g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 nay. Gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam S\u01b0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u1edbng ng\u1ea1i duy nh\u1ea5t, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng k\u1ef5 r\u01a1 xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111ang tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u00e0!&rdquo; &ndash; D\u00e2n Anh \u0111ang kh\u00e1o nhau n\u1eeda \u0111\u00f9a n\u1eeda th\u1eadt nh\u01b0 v\u1eady sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n \u1edf c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Colombia. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m-421-190321.html\" target=\"_blank\">L\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft thua tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m</span>.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1 b\u1ecf l\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua n\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t gieo r\u1eafc qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, d\u00e0n Tam S\u01b0 tr\u1ebb trung \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u00e2m l\u00fd v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1ea5n \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp t\u1eebng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh g\u1ee5c kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft bao nhi\u00eau th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 cha anh, xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a Colombia \u1edf ph\u00fat 90+3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Preview Thuy Dien vs Anh\" title=\"Preview Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 tr\u00ean m\u1ee9c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Anh ch\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi y\u00eau h\u1ecd th\u1ecfa m\u00e3n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t c\u1ea3m x\u00fac ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 y\u00ean l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u00fd tr\u00ed. Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb m\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t m\u1ed9t Panama qu\u00e1 y\u1ebfu \u0111u\u1ed1i, Tam S\u01b0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ph\u00e1 c\u00e1ch trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia hay c\u1ea3 Tunisia ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1eb3n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng Anh kh\u00e1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, ch\u1ec9 nh\u1edd m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i hay Harry Kane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-o-tran-colombia-vs-anh-nguoi-thu-linh-phot-tinh-ang-le-421-190324.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/du-am-colombia-vs-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/harry-kane-o-tran-colombia-vs-anh-nguoi-thu-linh-phot-tinh-ang-le-421-190324.html\">Harry Kane: G\u00e3 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh &ldquo;ph\u1edbt t\u1ec9nh \u0102ng-l\u00ea&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Jordan Pickford v\u1eabn x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n vinh nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t trong \u0111\u00eam l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, nh\u01b0ng sao ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e3ng qu\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay c\u1ea3 ni\u1ec1m t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o Harry Kane \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi \u1edf World Cup 2018 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o Tam S\u01b0 \u0111ang l\u1ec7 thu\u1ed9c th\u00e1i qu\u00e1 v\u00e0o ng\u00f4i sao Tottenham. M\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Tam S\u01b0 b\u1ecb ki\u1ec1m t\u1ecfa th\u00ec ngu\u1ed3n cung b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khai th\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n th\u00ec ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c, Anh ch\u1ec9 \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh, khi phong c\u00e1ch tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u1eabn t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u01a1n \u0111i\u1ec7u v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u00e9t. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 k\u1ebf s\u00e1ch taca-dada truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho m\u1ed9t Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao trung b\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh 21h00 ng\u00e0y 77 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh 21h00 ng\u00e0y 77 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Nhan-dinh-Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh-21h00-ngay-77-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Colombia tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft l\u00e0 c\u1eeda \u1ea3i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho Anh tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u1edf Moscow, nh\u01b0ng theo d\u00f5i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/du-am-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-nguoi-hung-emil-forsberg-421-190326.html\" target=\"_blank\">h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh phi th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n-kh\u00f4ng-Ibra</span> \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang \u0111i, gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u c\u00f3 l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00e1i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Tam S\u01b0. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Scandinavia \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n k\u1ef5 r\u01a1 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft nh\u1ed3i b\u00f3ng cho Zlatan \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecb b\u1eaft b\u00e0i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u1ed9t m\u00e0u \u0111\u00f3, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 h\u01a1n, khoa h\u1ecdc h\u01a1n v\u00e0 bi\u1ebfn h\u00f3a h\u01a1n. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y b\u1eb1ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-4-2 c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Janne Anderson ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng pressing t\u1eeb xa v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e2y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ngay t\u1eeb ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eabu nhi\u00ean m\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp lo\u1ea1i \u0110KV\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 3/4 tr\u1eadn \u1edf k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u x\u1ee9ng danh m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u1ef1a \u00f4 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u t\u00e1i l\u1eb7p chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch hi\u1ec3n h\u00e1ch n\u0103m x\u01b0a, t\u1eeb t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u0103m 1994 hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n n\u0103m 1958 khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ngay tr\u00ean qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh (21h00 ng\u00e0y 77) G\u1ecdi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh (21h00 ng\u00e0y 77) G\u1ecdi gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/Nhan-dinh-Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh-(21h00-ngay-77)-Goi-giac-mo-ve-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ch\u1ec9 e s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi tinh hoa c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 h\u1ebft c\u1ea3 ra cho \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n ngh\u00eanh chi\u1ebfn Anh t\u1ed1i nay. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i qua ch\u00e2n nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Emil Forsberg, trong khi Ola Toivonen hay Marcus Berg tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p cho \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">H\u1ec7 tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n c\u1ea3, \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd khuy\u1ebft \u0111i m\u1ed9t m\u1eaft x\u00edch ch\u1ee7 ch\u1ed1t \u1edf Samara khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Mikael Lustig b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1eed huy\u1ec7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u00edch c\u1ef1c khai th\u00e1c. B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec thay v\u00ec tranh ch\u1ea5p tay \u0111\u00f4i hay kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfn, t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 mi\u1ebfng \u0111\u00e1nh h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh g\u1ee5c Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n n\u1ebfu Tam S\u01b0 h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-nguoi-hung-emil-forsberg-421-190326.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/Nhan-dinh-Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh-(21h00-ngay-77)-Goi-giac-mo-ve-hinh-anh-2.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-nguoi-hung-emil-forsberg-421-190326.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n-kh\u00f4ng-Ibra ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf World Cup: H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh phi th\u01b0\u1eddng vi\u1ebft b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau h\u01a1n hai th\u1eadp k\u1ef7. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e0i v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i Zlatan...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1 d\u1edbp \u0111\u00e1 penalty \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau 12 n\u0103m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn knock-out \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup. Nh\u00e2n d\u00e2n x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 h\u1eb3n r\u1ea5t mong ng\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c sang trang l\u1ecbch s\u1eed, nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup (th\u1eafng v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 2/8 tr\u1eadn) \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t b\u00e1n k\u1ebft sau 28 n\u0103m k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Italia 90.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u00ean h\u1ebft, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Anh th\u1eafng v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1/9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c (World Cup v\u00e0 Euro). Hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 2002 v\u00e0 2006 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 hai tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0. L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">- Anh g\u1eb7p Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 24 l\u1ea7n, th\u1eafng 8 h\u00f2a 9 v\u00e0 thua 7. Trong \u0111\u00f3 v\u1edbi 8 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup v\u00e0 Euro, Anh ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 6 v\u00e0 thua 2.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">- Anh v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i, \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng n\u0103m 2002 v\u00e0 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng 2006.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">- Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup sau 12 n\u0103m, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 24 n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">- Anh t\u1eebng 8 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng hai trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, v\u1edbi n\u0103m 1966 th\u1eb3ng ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ngay tr\u00ean qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n (4-4-2): 1. Olsen; 16. Krafth &ndash; 3. Lindelof &ndash; 4. Granqvist &ndash; 6. Augustinsson; 17. Claesson &ndash; 7. Larsson &ndash; 8. Ekdal &ndash; 10. Forsberg; 20. Toivonen &ndash; 9. Berg<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh (3-5-2): 1. Pickford; 2. Walker &ndash; 5. Stones &ndash; 6. Maguire; 12. Trippier &ndash; 20. Alli &ndash; 8. Henderson &ndash; 7. Lingard &ndash; 3. Rose; 9. Kane &ndash; 10. Sterling<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh: Tam S\u01b0 th\u1eafng 1-0\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Doi hinh du kien Thuy Dien vs Anh\" title=\"\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh-(4-4-2-vs-3-5-2).png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"980","checkdouble":"190574"},{"date":"08:56 07/07","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i t\u00e2m l\u00fd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed v\u1edbi U19 Indonesia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/7/u19-viet-nam-thoai-mai-tam-ly-truoc-tran-cau-sinh-tu-voi-u19-indonesia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 h\u1ee9ng kh\u1edfi v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay 7/7.</h2><h2>U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 Indonesia</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 Indonesia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p U19 Indonesia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/36639412_226460401412200_5514359247783067648_n.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vui v\u1ebb trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a \u0110T ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia c\u00f9ng U19 Th\u00e1i Lan, th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 v\u1edbi \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i nay 7/7 m\u1edbi c\u1ea7m ch\u1eafc t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua 6/7, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp v\u1edbi t\u00e2m l\u00fd kh\u00e1 tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin, tr\u00e0n ng\u1eadp ti\u1ebfng c\u01b0\u1eddi. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u sinh t\u1eed v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 U19 Indonesia.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Indonesia, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Vi\u1ec7t Nam. \u1ede ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, n\u1ebfu d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp chi\u1ec1u qua, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trau chu\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Do \u0111\u00e2y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1eeb c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u00ean HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a kh\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p nhau c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ea1 Indonesia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1ebb, s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 l\u1edbn. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi U19 Indonesia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 19h ng\u00e0y 7/7, tr\u00ean SV\u0110 Gelora Delta.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bongda24h c\u0169ng s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Mong b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-dung-truoc-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-tuc-gian-voi-hoc-tro-168-190501.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/u19-viet-nam-dung-truoc-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-tuc-gian-voi-hoc-tro.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/u19-viet-nam-dung-truoc-nguy-co-bi-loai-hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-tuc-gian-voi-hoc-tro-168-190501.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u1edbi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-19h00-ngay-77-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-344-190577.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/nhan-dinh-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-19h00-ngay-77-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-bong-da/nhan-dinh-u19-viet-nam-vs-u19-indonesia-19h00-ngay-77-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-344-190577.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Indonesia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7 (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nU19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs U19 Indonesia l\u00fac 19h00 ng\u00e0y 7/7 (V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-41-u19-lao-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190441.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-41-u19-lao-u19-dong-nam-a-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-u19-viet-nam-41-u19-lao-u19-dong-nam-a-2018-325-190441.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 4-1 U19 L\u00e0o (U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018)</span><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm U19 L\u00e0o \u1edf tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Indonesia.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-dang-tiec-truoc-u19-thai-lan-168-190139.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-dang-tiec-truoc-u19-thai-lan.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-hoang-anh-tuan-noi-gi-sau-tran-hoa-dang-tiec-truoc-u19-thai-lan-168-190139.html\">HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc tr\u01b0\u1edbc U19 Th\u00e1i Lan?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, HLV U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u00f4ng Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"979","checkdouble":"190579"},{"date":"04:26 07/07","title":"T\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil, Kevin de Bruyne n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/toa-sang-truoc-brazil-kevin-de-bruyne-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kevin de Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u1ea1 Selecao \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kevin de Bruyne ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brazil, HLV Roberto Martinez \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed Lukaku d\u1ea1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f2n De Bruyne b\u00f3 v\u00e0o trong nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 9 \u1ea3o. C\u00e1ch s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u HLV Everton \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e1t huy r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kevin de Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kevin de Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/Kevin-de-Bruyne-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Brazil-vs-Bi-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Bruyne ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brazil</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Bruyne v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u1eef b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t li\u00ean t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m kh\u1ed5 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng x\u1ed9c th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1eb7c ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 30, t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng nhanh, Lukaku \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 De Bruyne x\u1eed l\u00fd k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City \u0111em l\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-chu-y-trong-tran-brazil-vs-bi-421-190555.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Brazil vs B\u1ec9 </span>ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 3 l\u1ea7n, 2 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Ngo\u00e0i ra anh c\u00f2n c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. De Bruyne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>De Bruyne tin B\u1ec9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kevin de Bruyne ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9, ng\u00f4i sao 27 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap B\u1ea7y qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf h\u1ea1 Selecao \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Bruyne noi ve tran Brazil vs Bi\" title=\"De Bruyne n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/toa-sang-truoc-brazil-kevin-de-bruyne-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>De Bruyne n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Brazil vs B\u1ec9</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, trong 30 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n, nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng s\u1edbm gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Brazil \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt trong hi\u1ec7p hai, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBrazil \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda B\u1ec9, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t trong 15 ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n B\u1ec9 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd, B\u1ec9 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"978","checkdouble":"190557"}]}